-- ============================================================================
-- Ragebot Aimbot v3.0 (FIXED, consolidated single-version)
-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- This file consolidates v1-v5 of the original rba2.lua and fixes 30+ critical
-- bugs identified during code review. Highlights:
--
--   * Single script (no duplicate execution / leaked connections)
--   * Proper target stickiness (file-scope lastTargetTime, identity comparison)
--   * Magnitude-based stabilization (NOT broken angle scaling)
--   * Cached ESP Drawings (no per-frame Highlight churn)
--   * Camera-type set to Scriptable when "Camera" aim mode is used
--   * World-yaw + local-pitch camera rotation (correct under roll)
--   * AssemblyLinearVelocity fallback chain (Velocity is deprecated)
--   * RaycastFilterType.Exclude (Blacklist is deprecated)
--   * Custom GUI drag (Draggable is deprecated/hidden)
--   * Robust executor-unload hook (Synapse/Solara/Krnl/Xeno patterns)
--   * Slider connections tracked in global Connections table
--   * pcall-guarded init with bounded retries
--   * Hotkeys ignored while typing in chat
--   * Mouse-inset corrected (GetMouseLocation vs WorldToViewportPoint)
--   * Team-check handles nil teams (nil == nil was true)
--   * Visibility raycast uses IsDescendantOf(player.Character)
--   * SafeTracerOrigin with default fallback
--   * Math.abs for ESP box dimensions (ragdoll-safe)
--   * LocalPlayer.Character nil-guarded in ESP distance calc
--   * AutoAdjust UI sync (sliders reflect auto-adjusted values)
--   * All task.* APIs (no legacy delay/wait)
-- ============================================================================

